[
    {
        "text": "Overwork in Japan is a real problem and a deadly one at that.",
        "startTime": 511,
        "endTime": 4256,
        "slowStartTime": 916,
        "slowEndTime": 6609
    },
    {
        "text": "There is even a Japanese word for it,...",
        "startTime": 4667,
        "endTime": 6349,
        "slowStartTime": 7151,
        "slowEndTime": 9748
    },
    {
        "text": "...\"karoshi\" meaning \"death from overwork.\"",
        "startTime": 6559,
        "endTime": 9445,
        "slowStartTime": 9989,
        "slowEndTime": 14393
    },
    {
        "text": "It's a problem that affects Japan's teachers in particular.",
        "startTime": 9925,
        "endTime": 12873,
        "slowStartTime": 15038,
        "slowEndTime": 19535
    },
    {
        "text": "They are expected to not just teach their students...",
        "startTime": 13292,
        "endTime": 15825,
        "slowStartTime": 20088,
        "slowEndTime": 23962
    },
    {
        "text": "...but also lead them during after-school activities,...",
        "startTime": 15897,
        "endTime": 18833,
        "slowStartTime": 23995,
        "slowEndTime": 28474
    },
    {
        "text": "...cleaning duties and mentoring.",
        "startTime": 19195,
        "endTime": 21067,
        "slowStartTime": 28942,
        "slowEndTime": 31826
    },
    {
        "text": "One investigation found school teachers...",
        "startTime": 21433,
        "endTime": 23511,
        "slowStartTime": 32299,
        "slowEndTime": 35492
    },
    {
        "text": "...working an average of 123 hours overtime each month,...",
        "startTime": 23623,
        "endTime": 28354,
        "slowStartTime": 35584,
        "slowEndTime": 42756
    },
    {
        "text": "...well above the government-defined karoshi line of 80 hours,...",
        "startTime": 28761,
        "endTime": 32812,
        "slowStartTime": 43292,
        "slowEndTime": 49443
    },
    {
        "text": "...essentially meaning a high risk of death from overwork...",
        "startTime": 33227,
        "endTime": 36239,
        "slowStartTime": 49990,
        "slowEndTime": 54583
    },
    {
        "text": "...if one works more than 80 overtime hours a month.",
        "startTime": 36503,
        "endTime": 40174,
        "slowStartTime": 54905,
        "slowEndTime": 60486
    },
    {
        "text": "For some teachers, though, that risk does turn real.",
        "startTime": 40444,
        "endTime": 44125,
        "slowStartTime": 60816,
        "slowEndTime": 66413
    },
    {
        "text": "A brain hemorrhage killed middle school teacher Yoshio Kudo in 2007...",
        "startTime": 46001,
        "endTime": 51315,
        "slowStartTime": 69152,
        "slowEndTime": 77198
    },
    {
        "text": "...at just 40 years of age.",
        "startTime": 51608,
        "endTime": 52943,
        "slowStartTime": 77562,
        "slowEndTime": 79639
    },
    {
        "text": "His diary entries told of a punishing workday that started early...",
        "startTime": 53379,
        "endTime": 57357,
        "slowStartTime": 80219,
        "slowEndTime": 86261
    },
    {
        "text": "...and could last until nearly midnight.",
        "startTime": 57453,
        "endTime": 59459,
        "slowStartTime": 86329,
        "slowEndTime": 89414
    },
    {
        "text": "Teachers are particularly vulnerable to karoshi.",
        "startTime": 60221,
        "endTime": 62839,
        "slowStartTime": 90481,
        "slowEndTime": 94484
    },
    {
        "text": "A decades-old law essentially prevents them from being paid for overtime.",
        "startTime": 63315,
        "endTime": 66935,
        "slowStartTime": 95123,
        "slowEndTime": 100627
    },
    {
        "text": "His widow, a former teacher herself,...",
        "startTime": 68017,
        "endTime": 70210,
        "slowStartTime": 102175,
        "slowEndTime": 105540
    },
    {
        "text": "...says attitudes to karoshi need to change.",
        "startTime": 70724,
        "endTime": 74399,
        "slowStartTime": 106236,
        "slowEndTime": 111823
    },
    {
        "text": "For about a year before he passed away,...",
        "startTime": 76191,
        "endTime": 78409,
        "slowStartTime": 114436,
        "slowEndTime": 117839
    },
    {
        "text": "...he would often say how tired he was and how bad a headache he had...",
        "startTime": 78717,
        "endTime": 82432,
        "slowStartTime": 118226,
        "slowEndTime": 123873
    },
    {
        "text": "...from when he moved to the new school in April until he died two months later.",
        "startTime": 83131,
        "endTime": 87318,
        "slowStartTime": 124847,
        "slowEndTime": 131202
    },
    {
        "text": "He kept saying he was exhausted.",
        "startTime": 87541,
        "endTime": 89217,
        "slowStartTime": 131461,
        "slowEndTime": 134050
    },
    {
        "text": "He said he wanted to leave the school.",
        "startTime": 89449,
        "endTime": 91125,
        "slowStartTime": 134323,
        "slowEndTime": 136913
    }
]